  <section class="section">
    <p class="section-label">Our service</p>
    <h2>What We Clean in Riddells Creek</h2>
    <p>
      We clean chimneys, flues and wood heaters for homes throughout Riddells Creek VIC 3431. Whether you've got an open fireplace, a freestanding wood heater or an older setup that hasn't been serviced in years, we'll clean it properly and tell you exactly what we find.
    </p>
    <div class="service-grid">
      <div class="service-card">
