    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <p class="section-label">When to book</p>
    <h2>Reasons Riddells Creek Homeowners Call Us</h2>
    <p>
      A lot of bookings happen before winter, but plenty also come after people notice something just isn't working as cleanly as it should.
    </p>
    <ul class="check-list">
      <li>The fireplace is smoking back into the room</li>
      <li>The draw feels weaker than it used to</li>
      <li>There's a stronger smell coming from the flue</li>
      <li>The heater has been used heavily through winter</li>
      <li>The chimney hasn't been cleaned in a long time</li>
