    <div class="about-card">
      <p>
        Daves Chimney Sweeping is owner-operated. When you call, you're dealing directly with the business — not a call centre or franchise booking line. We service Riddells Creek VIC 3431 and surrounding areas with straightforward local service.
      </p>
      <p>
        We keep things simple: clear communication, fast quotes and a proper clean without the runaround.
      </p>
      <div class="about-detail">
